data.description: Discover the charms of this three-bedroom, two-bathroom home featuring a spacious floor plan, vaulted ceilings, and a separate dining room. The residence boasts updated exterior and interior lighting, along with upgraded remote-controlled interior ceiling fans for added convenience. Relax in the jetted tub and walk-in shower, and appreciate the practicality of a separate laundry room. The split floor plan enhances privacy, while the garage floor is equipped with an epoxy coating for a polished finish. Step outside to a large fenced-in backyard, providing both privacy and ample outdoor space for various activities. With these features, this home combines modern upgrades with thoughtful design elements for comfortable and enjoyable living.
